  "text": "The design parametric model is generated from the customer's facial measurements (Fig. 3) . The eyeglass frame model consists of a rim, a temple and a bridge. The shape of the rim is formed by Riesenfeld spline curves [CITATION_1] . A rectangular region bordered by the lines l i (i = 1,...,4) is defined around the user's eye as follows.",
